HEADWORD: Dismarry
<hw>Dis*mar"ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>dis-</ets> + <ets>marry</ets>: cf. OF. <ets>desmarier</ets>, F.
<ets>d⟦eacute⟧marier</ets>.]</ety> <def>To free from the bonds of
